n</a><br>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.rebol.org/documentation.r?script=aclock-p.r">documentation</a></td><td style="text-align: right;font-size: 85%" class="lsdata2">3.5&nbsp;KB<br>20&nbsp;Sep&nbsp;2004</td><td class="lsdata2 code" style="padding:1em;">aproximate an analog clock and add alarm<br><span style="font-weight:bold">author: Tom Conlin</span><div style="border-top: thin blue solid; margin:1em" class="lsdata2">Discussion posts: 98.  Latest by: janwil on 8-Apr.</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan="3" style="border-bottom: thin blue solid !important; padding-top: 1em" class="lsdata1">make-doc-pro</td></tr><tr><td class="lsdata1"><a href="http://www.rebol.org/view-script.r?script=make-doc-pro.r">make-doc-pro.r</a><br>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.rebol.org/discussion.r?script=make-doc-pro.r">discussion</a><br>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.rebol.org/documentation.r?script=make-doc-pro.r">documentation</a></td><td style="text-align: right;font-size: 85%" class="lsdata1">v:1.0.8<br>57.8&nbsp;KB<br>7&nbsp;Feb&nbsp;2004</td><td class="lsdata1 code" style="padding:1em;">Parses the make-doc-pro markup language into a
